name: My 5SOS - A Fun Game for 5 Seconds of Summer
name_original: My 5SOS - A Fun Game for 5 Seconds of Summer
description:
Play as your favorite 5SOS member in a simple 1-touch challenging game.

Unlock new worlds, songs, clothes, characters, enemies and a lot of other amazing features!

Experience a lot of amazing and super addictive game modes!

* Disclaimer: this app is not affiliated with or endorsed by 5 Seconds of Summer, the individual members, or anyone associated with the production of the band.
